title: Use build flavors to provide a Google-less build
message:
Use build flavors to provide a Google-less build

This commit uses build flavors to provide two different builds: A 'base'
build and a 'google' build.

The 'base' build builds a basic verison of the app with no dependencies
on Google Play Services.

The 'google' build uses Google Play Services to adds some extra services
(Firebase crash reporting, ability to donate to the developer).

title: Allow non-release builds without a keystore
message:
Allow non-release builds without a keystore

This commit allows Gradle to build the app in a non-release
configuration, even if the keystore file doesn't exist.
